## Installation

```bash
openclaw plugins install {{NPM_SCOPE}}/{{CHANNEL_ID}}
```

## Configuration

Add to your OpenClaw config (`~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`):

```json
{
  "plugins": {
    "entries": {
      "{{CHANNEL_ID}}": {
        "enabled": true
      }
    }
  },
  "channels": {
    "{{CHANNEL_ID}}": {
      "enabled": true,
      "TODO": "Add channel-specific config"
    }
  }
}
```

