## Development

### Run Tests

```bash
npm test
```

### Run Tests in Watch Mode

```bash
npm run test:watch
```

### Local Development

```bash
# Link to local OpenClaw
cd /path/to/openclaw
openclaw plugins install /path/to/this/plugin
```

